response.overview: Raven’s plan is firmly in place. his young, acolyte is chosen, and Raven is ready to pay homage to the wonderful oddness of the recently departed Bowie by resurrecting his invention…Ziggy Stardust. Uh, one problem…this kid has no idea what any of that is.  Join Raven as he attempts to spark new life into a young worker in search of a character. It’s another makeover…Raven style!
response.title: Raven’s Restler Rescue: EP 3 – Ziggy
